        <h1>Besan Chilla</h1>
       
        <div class="recipe-details">
         <img src="besan-chilla.jpg" alt="Besan Chilla" class="recipe-image">
            <div class="ingredients">
                <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>1 cup chickpea flour</li>
                    <li>1/2 cup grated zucchini</li>
                    <li>1/2 cup spinach, chopped</li>
                    <li>1 tsp cumin powder</li>
                    <li>1/2 tsp turmeric</li>
                    <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
                    <li>Water as needed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="instructions">
                <h2>Instructions:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Mix chickpea flour, zucchini, spinach, cumin, turmeric, salt, and pepper in a bowl.</li>
                    <li>Add water gradually to form a pancake batter consistency.</li>
                    <li>Heat a pan and pour a ladle of batter onto the pan, cooking for 2-3 minutes on each side.</li>
                    <li>Serve hot with chutney or yogurt.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
